msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 26. Sotāpannasutta → soto or sotāpanno (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Sotāpannasutta "
msgstr "26. A Stream-Enterer "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn48.26:1.1"
msgid "“Chayimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these six faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.26:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "sn48.26:1.3"
msgid "Cakkhundriyaṃ … pe … manindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "The faculties of the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind. "

msgctxt "sn48.26:1.4"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako imesaṃ channaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti—"
msgstr "A noble disciple comes to truly understand these six faculties’ origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape. "

msgctxt "sn48.26:1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako sotāpanno avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo”ti. "
msgstr "Such a noble disciple is called a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.26:1.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

